version: 0.1
This package used to convert ship linesplan data to .pat file.
Basic nested structure of previous MATLAB code is:

start.m yes|
        | load_linesplan.m yes|
                           | scale_linesplan.m yes
                           | scaling factors yes|
                                             | mesh_gui.m  Pending
                                             | KG yes
                                             | Kxx yes
                                             | Kyy yes |
                                                   | linesplan_size.m yes
                                                   | Kxx, Kyy, KG yes |
                                                   | water_depth yes |
                                                                 | mesh_linesplan.m (without user inputs)? draft changes?
                                                                 | mesh_linesplan2.m (with user inputs)?

